name: On The Payroll Of The Trade Federation
Lore: 'A political agenda is no use without supporters. And in the world of politics, left and right often meet in the middle.',
Text: 'Target an opponent''s character at Galactic Senate if you have a senator there with a matching agenda. For remainder of turn: your senator''s politics is increased by target''s current politics, and target''s politics is then reduced to zero.',
